snippet.title: Spin Rhythm XD Nintendo Switch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Kinetic rhythm action spins onto Nintendo Switch October 26. Now with local multiplayer (up to 4 players!)

Enjoy motion controls with Joy-Cons or Switch Pro controllers
You can even use a keyboard and mouse on Switch!

Available 26 October in all regions. Pre-order available 1 week earlier.
